  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So on we go in the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm living in Whitestone, part of Flushing, New York, and in this little town where people were not aware of refugees, wars, and I don't believe there were any Jewish people living in this town as well.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A very close knit place, and one morning very soon after arriving, my uncle took me to school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, you must understand, my older cousin there, a female who was 14, cheerfully put on makeup and pretended she didn't know me.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My other cousin, unfortunately-- the younger one-- was in bed with rheumatic fever and was not able-- she had to be very quiet, and she really wasn't available for a whole lot.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But a wonderful wardrobe was there, and my aunt used to iron things by the hour and hang them into her closet.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And very carefully, every so often, I would ask my aunt whether I could wear one of those skirts or one of those shoes to school and was always told, no, that was impossible.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so therefore, off I went to school in long knit brown stockings, and high shoes that were laced beyond the ankle, and some very typical European and old fashioned looking clothes.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And really felt like somebody from outer space, perhaps.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't think they looked like that, though.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my uncle took me to school, left me in the principal's office to register my attendance and so forth.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And of course, I was given a test.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I couldn't speak English.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I can't imagine how I understood the things that were being said to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I think my uncle did a little bit of translation.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
